description: Ten years have passed since Nathan , following a scientific expedition of the Museum of Worlds in the torrid equatorial forests of Diamond Point , has witnessed an extraordinary event , what is commonly called a " close encounter of the third kind " , ie direct contact with extraterrestrial life forms . The members of the expedition , in fact , had attended a mission to recover a large number of alien bodies fallen on our planet. On that occasion the Alfa agent had made ​​the acquaintance of a certain Holt , a friendly local crook , who was also incredulous audience of the event. Now Holt is addressed to the Alfa Agency to investigate the disappearance of his business partner Rico , firmly convinced that aliens are back on Earth ... And the facts seem to prove him right, with the difference that this time the goal of these beings could be the total annihilation of the human race ...
name: L’inafferrabile

description:
Green Lantern: Secret Origin: Part 7 of 7

Atrocitus has been defeated, but now Hal Jordan and Sinestro have to face their greatest threat to date - the Guardians of the Green Lantern Corps!

Green Lantern: Alienated: Part 1 of 3

With Hal Jordan back as Earth's Green Lantern, it's time for a NEW adventure - featuring psychotic telepath Hector Hammond and fellow Corpser Kilowog!

The Flash: Case One: The Dastardly Death of the Rogues: Part 6 of 6

Barry Allen's first case since his return comes to a stunning conclusion - but the timeline will never be the same!

Batman and Robin #13: Batman and Robin Must Die - Part One: The Garden Of Death

The Joker, posing as crime writer Oberton Sexton has been leading the Dynamic Duo a merry dance. But Robin is baying for blood. Has the Joker played his hand too soon?

Batman: The Return of Bruce Wayne - Part Three: The Bones of Bristol Bay

Swirling through time, clutching at wisps of a forgotten identity, Bruce Wayne is finally washed up on the shore of Bristol Bay and lands at the feet of the world's most famous pirate!

Batman 700: Time and the Batman - Yesterday

In a homage to the Silver Age of Batman our dynamic duo find themselves at the mercy of the Joker, who, with the help of the 'Maybe Machine', might obliterate them all!

description:
Batman in London! Panic of the Composite Creature

You've seen the cartoon - now the official comic is here! The first issue of Batman: The Brave and the Bold brings you a brand new comic strip - a tale of terror and adventure from the streets of London, as a frightening freak of nature runs riot in England's capital city! Can Bats and Power Girl keep him away from the crown jewels?

Win awesome stuff!

In each issue of Batman: The Brave and the Bold we'll be giving you the chance to win some very cool prizes. First up - we have some fantastic packs of figures to give away thanks to our amazing friends at Mattel. Look out for details of how to enter inside the first issue!

Green Arrow! Power Girl! Aquaman! Who's Who?

Dive into the all-action crime-fighting world of Batman: The Brave and the Bold, as we bring you awesome hero and villain profiles in every issue! Find out who can control the minds of his victims, who can turn her foes to ice with her freezing breath, who can communicate with every creature under the sea, and loads more cool facts!
name: Batman in London! Panic of the Composite Creature

volume.name: Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description:
Brand New Comic Strip! Menace of the Time Thief!

Issue three of Batman: The Brave and the Bold blasts onto a comics shelf near you with a brand new burst of adventure! Dive beneath the waves with Aquaman in 'Menace of the Time Thief!', as he and The Caped Crusader are thrown through the ages!

Bat Signals

Awesome art and letters from awesome readers! Check out the comic's 'Bat Signals' section and start getting creative so that you can feature in it next time! The address to send stuff to is on the right - so, no excuses, grab your pens and pencils and get scribbling!

Batman's Secret Files: Aquaman

He's super-strong. He can breathe underwater. He can communicate with - and control - the creatures beneath the sea. He's also the King of Atlantis. No wonder Aquaman has boundless confidence! Find out all about Batman's good-natured ally in the latest issue!
name: Menace of the Time Thief!

volume.name: Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description:
Brand New Comic Strip! The Attack of the Virtual Villains

El Paso, Texas is the setting for a brand new comic strip featuring only in Batman: The Brave and the Bold Comic! A digital villain is on the rampage in the real world - can Batman and Blue Beetle get to the bottom of a crazy game quest, or will they run out of health points first?

Win Awesome Toys!

We have FIVE fantastic prize packs to give away in the latest issue of Batman: The Brave and the Bold Comic - thanks to our friends at Mattel. Don't miss your chance to win a Stretch Attack Battle Packs, Deluxe Figures with cool accessories, and two Basic Figures from Mattel's awesome new range!

Batman's Secret Files: Blue Beetle

Powered with science from beyond the stars, Jaime Reyes is just a normal teen looking to make a name for himself among his super-hero idols! Not only does the astonishing Blue Beetle get a starring role in the latest issue's comic strip, there's an in-depth profile of his powers, too!
name: The Attack of the Virtual Villains

volume.name: Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description:
Brand New Comic Strip! A Batman's Work Is Never Done

Batman: The Brave and the Bold is back for a stunning issue #4, now crammed with more features, puzzles and profiles than ever before! It's Sunday night and another (not so) regular week lies ahead for The Caped Crusader in an all-new, action-packed comic strip story!

Batman's Secret Files: The Atom

Get the lowdown on Batman's shape shifting ally The Atom in the new issue! Diminutive scientist Ray Palmer can shrink his body to varying degrees and manipulate his weight to his advantage. He can also rearrange molecules on a subatomic level, creating new isotopes from atomic raw material!
name: A Batman's Work Is Never Done

Plus:

  • Batman's Vehicles: Check out the Batmobile, the Batplane, and the Batcopter!

Build Your Own Batmobile!

There's a reason that Batman is able to travel all over the world fighting crime - he has the coolest set of wheels around! Follow our simple instructions and you can build your very own Batmobile!

Batman's Greatest Moments: Part One

Batman isn't just a hero, he's the hero for other superheroes! Follow our guide to the coolest things that the Caped Crusader has ever done in the latest issue of Batman: The Brave and The Bold!

description:
A re-issue of Lenore #2.1 featuring brand new cover art by Roman Dirge, released to mark the return of the cute little dead girl in a long-awaited new issue of the comic.

The shocking secret of Lenore's rebirth is revealed in 'The Macabre Malevolence Of Mortimer Fledge'.
name: The Macabre Malevolence Of Mortimer Fledge

description: Lenore's long-awaited comeback in 'Where The Flutter Ends'. After years of shocking physical and mental abuse, extreme violence and unnecessary brutality, could Mr. Gosh’s feelings of unrequited love for Lenore have finally turned?
name: Where The Flutter Ends

description:
The legendary, unstoppable, bucket-headed, demonic, bounty-hunter Pooty Applewater, Dark Minion from the 9th Layer of Heck is back with his lethal tiny pitchfork of death ready to do his master, The Dark Overlord's bidding!

Once before the paths of Lenore and Pooty crossed and the forces of Heck were unleashed. Oceans boiled, mountains crumbled and an army of Nazi zombies were slaughtered by a handsome vampire and some of Taxidermy's mates from next door.

But now Pooty is back, and the question on everyone's lips is Where Pooty At? Indeed! Where has that bucket headed uber warrior with a passion for Parcheesi been and why is he back and what does his return spell for Lenore, the cute little dead girl?
name: Where Pooty At?

description: Inspired by The Unforgiving, the newest album from Within Temptation! A powerful medium, Mother Maiden recruits lost souls to be part of her wraith taskforce to fight evil in all its forms. They each carry a specific guilt about something they did in their lives. Mother Maiden offers them an opportunity to 'make right what is wrong' by giving them missions and assignments to hunt down evil as a penance for their previous sins.
name: Perdition + Penance: Part 1

description: Nathan Never continues the hunt for the dangerous alien criminal Dehm , who arrived on Earth with anything but peaceful purposes .  While in Diamond Point the preparations for the festivities of New Year are underway , Dehm endeavors , leaving behind a long trail of blood , to complete the mad attempt to eradicate the human race from the planet , a massacre to offer as a sacrifice to evil god Yaab . Only with the help of extraterrestrial s a gents Roxy and Raz , Nathan has a hope of stopping the Dehm 's doomsday plan , in a mission made ​​even more complicated by the ability of the alien to " occupy" the bodies of his victims.
name: La torre dell’orologio

description: George Sad , meek appearance ​​and sad expression , is a retired secret agent . Once enrolled in the Intelligence of the space station , he has seen the world around him suddenly changing , unable to adapt to these new rhythms and embrace these new moral , became a cumbersome relic of bygone days. So he was given the heave-ho , a pat on the back and probably a gold watch with an inscription on the generic case. But George never stopped fighting , and when his friend is killed by the police with the infamous accusation of terrorism, he falls back on the field, this time asking for help from Solomon  Darver and his famous Alfa Agency . And, accompanied by an expert agent like Nathan Never , the old fox of the Secret Service shows that he still has a lot of arrows to his bow.
name: La guerra segreta

description: The one name that still speaks volumes of how absolute power can corrupt – Caligula. Things in Rome are reaching the breaking point. Caligula’s madness is becoming apparent to some. He must go. However successfully acting on it is a very different matter. Virgin blood ceremonies, gladiator fights rigged for added brutality, and dinner parties where guests are randomly slaughtered, is there any limit to Caligula’s depravity? Can Felix keep his focus and sanity in the face of so much misery and horror?

Darth Vader confronts a deadly assassin . . . . . . the outlaw crew of the Uhumele arrives at the scene of Jedi Dass Jennir's last adventure-but Jennir is already gone . . . . . . and half a galaxy away, Imperial fighters are shot out of the sky by an 'unarmed' pleasure craft . . . Return to the dark times, that uncharted era of Star Wars history when the Empire was new and the Jedi were hunted by Darth Vader!
name: Part One (of Five)

volume.name: Star Wars: Dark Times - Out of the Wilderness

description:
Usagi Tsukino is a normal girl until she meets up with Luna, a talking cat, who tells her that she is Sailor Moon. As Sailor Moon, Usagi must fight evil and enforce justice, in the name of the moon and the mysterious moon princess. She meets other girls destined to be Sailor Senshi (Sailor Scouts), and together, they fight the forces of evil!

This new edition of Sailor Moon will feature:

  • An entirely new, incredibly accurate translation!
  • Japanese-style right-to-left reading!
  • New cover art never before seen in the United States!
  • The original Japanese character names!
  • Detailed translation notes!

This version of Sailor Moon will be completely true to the original. Join us as Sailor Moon returns to the U.S. for the first time in years!
name: Vol. 1

description: Usagi Tsukino is a normal girl until she meets up with Luna, a talking cat, who tells her that she is Sailor Moon. As Sailor Moon, Usagi must fight evils and enforce justice, in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. She meets other girls destined to be Sailor Senshi (Sailor Scouts), and together, they fight the forces of evil!
name: Vol. 2

description:
Tuxedo Mask gone bad!? As more of her closest allies fall under the power of the evil Queen Beryl, Usagi comes closer to discovering the truth behind her past. The stage is set for an all out battle for the fate of earth between the sailor guardians and the forces of evil. But when the dust settles, a little girl calling herself "Usagi" falls from the sky and right into the arms of Mamoru. What is her connection to Sailor Moon and why does she want the legendary silver crystal?

The new edition of Sailor Moon features:

- An entirely new, incredibly accurate translation

- Japanese style right to left reading

- New cover art never before seen in the US

- The original Japanese character names

- Detailed translation notes
name: Vol. 3

description:
A new group calling themselves Black Moon is after Usagi and the rest of the Sailor Guardians, wielding a new power known only as Malefic Black Crystal. Chibi-Usa may be the key to it all, but to find the answers and rescue her kidnapped friends, Usagi will have to journey through time to the 30th century and discover what fate has in store.

This new edition of Sailor Moon features

- An entirely new, incredibly accurate translations

- Japanese style, right to left reading

- New cover art never before seen in the US

- The original Japanese character names

- Detailed translation notes
name: Vol. 4

description:
Like Sailor Moon, Minako Aino is a normal thirteen year old schoolgirl until a faithful day when a white cat introduces himself to her and tells her she has the power to transform into the hero, Sailor V. Using a magic pen to transform, Sailor V fights the evil agents of the Dark Agency as she strives to protect the earth.

Codename: Sailor V, created by the author before she created the mega-popular Sailor Moon, has never before been available in the United States. This book features:

  • An incredibly accurate translation!
  • Japanese style, right to left reading!
  • New cover art never before seen in the United States!
  • The original Japanese character names!
  • Detailed translation notes!
name: Codename Sailor V

description: Like Sailor Moon, Minako Aino is a normal 13-year-old schoolgirl until a fateful day when a white cat introduces himself to her and tells her she has the power to transform into the hero, Sailor V. Using a magic pen to transform, Sailor V fights the evil agents of the Dark Agency as she strives to protect the earth.
name: Codename Sailor V

description: The Prometheus Corporation, during its deep sea exploration, unearths an ancient threat. Humankind is thrown into a battle for survival.

Detective Beecham feels she's losing her mind. After a hunter stumbles upon the latest Disciple victim, Beecham is herself attacked by The Triplets. Shaken but undeterred, Detective Beecham soldiers on. Her driving force? Finding Disciple - the one who took her daughter Rorey away - and making him pay!

The 2nd in Within Temptation's Series.

Includes QR Code link to an Exclusive Soundtrack
name: Penance: Part 2
